feedback_text: I attended a session recently, and I must say, I was pleasantly surprised by how supportive the team was. They explained everything so well and made sure we all understood before moving on. I did feel like we ran out of time too quickly, though, and would have liked a bit more hands-on practice.

I can't praise this team enough! They created such a relaxed and friendly atmosphere, which really helped me feel at ease. Learning new skills can be daunting, but they made it enjoyable. I left with a new sense of confidence!

My experience at DigiKnow was a blend of strengths and weaknesses. I appreciated the supportive atmosphere and innovative approach present during the session, which added genuine value. However, the occurrence of chaotic organization and unclear explanations at key moments detracted from the overall experience. There were instances when the instructors exhibited well-structured workshops, yet these were sometimes overshadowed by disorganized sessions. Overall, the session left me with mixed feelings about the effectiveness of the program. The session was helpful, and I learned something new, but I think there’s room for improvement. Perhaps more structured lessons or smaller groups would make things even better.
